      <title>阿拉伯国家拒绝特朗普重新安置巴勒斯坦人的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/arab-nations-reject-trump-s-idea-of-relocating-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提出将加沙巴勒斯坦人大规模迁移至埃及和约旦的建议，遭到几个阿拉伯国家以及阿拉伯联盟的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/arab-nations-reject-trump-s-idea-of-relocating-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 14:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼表示将在内华达州重新组建管理公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/ackman-says-he-s-reincorporating-management-company-in-nevada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁对冲基金经理比尔·阿克曼在 X 上回复有关公司离开特拉华州的帖子时表示：“我们正在内华达州重新注册我们的管理公司。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/ackman-says-he-s-reincorporating-management-company-in-nevada</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 14:08:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
