      <title>挪威释放与瑞典-拉脱维亚电缆损坏有关的船只</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/norway-releases-ship-linked-to-sweden-latvia-cable-damage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威北部地区当局释放了一艘涉嫌在波罗的海造成最新一次数据电缆泄露的船只，并称没有发现任何证据表明该船与此次事件有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/norway-releases-ship-linked-to-sweden-latvia-cable-damage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 13:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
